description:
he Autonomy token is an ERC-20 utility token which can be used for exchanging services on the Autonomy blockchain, such as:
- Pay for transportation services provided by autonomous vehicles, for parking, recharging, insurance and other services
- Receive ATNMY tokens for sharing traffic data with the smart-city infrastructure or other traffic participants (this is completely optional; data is aggregated & non-identifiable)
- Purchase access to above traffic data to improve the road conditions & receive alerts

The Autonomy token is not a security, an investment or a share in the company building Autonomy. It is a utility token, certified by a reputable law firm in Singapore as being compliant with the Singapore Law with regards to Utility Tokens. It DOES NOT pay dividends, interest and it does not offer any rights to ownership or decision making in the company building Autonomy. The token will be used and exchanged for services provided on the Autonomy blockchain network.
name: Autonomy Chain
